Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.43,0:00:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! You dropped this.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.38,0:00:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so clumsy. Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.17,0:00:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bad luck to drop\N your exam success charm.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.34,0:00:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.66,0:00:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.28,0:00:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My auntie asked me to buy it.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.52,0:00:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Her brother is taking the First Higher School {entrance }exam. {ichiko is abbreviation of https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/First_Higher_School}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.20,0:00:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you shouldn't tell them you dropped it.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.32,0:00:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, good idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.21,0:00:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.70,0:01:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.76,0:01:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenkichi, you're early. Come in.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.71,0:01:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for putting up with me this year, Sis. {/taking care of me/ doing *something* for me}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.61,0:01:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be your study room.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.73,0:01:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start right now and study\N until your husband gets home. {since the girl earlier said her aunt's younger brother is taking the exam, when he says nee-san, it's most likely because she his blood-related sister, and this nii-san is her husband, not his blood-related brother}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.83,0:01:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sounds good.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.85,0:01:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.65,0:01:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Who could that be?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.08,0:01:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? He just got here,\N and he's already studying?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.59,0:01:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but the test is pretty soon, \Nso he's in crunch mode.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.91,0:01:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard getting into prep school, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.78,0:02:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You mind if I say hello to him? {/peek on him}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.47,0:02:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I also wanted to give this to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.06,0:02:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.10,0:02:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt your studying{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.29,0:02:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I-It's you!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My! So it's you!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's how it is?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.82,0:02:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're taking the First entrance exam?\N You must be smart.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.41,0:02:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. Anyone can {\i1}take{\i0} the test.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.92,0:02:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know that you're going to pass.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.65,0:02:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but I failed it last year.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.80,0:02:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my second try.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.07,0:02:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Plenty of people only pass it \Non their second try.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.30,0:02:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, with my support, \Nyou're sure to pass!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.50,0:02:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.87,0:03:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, with my support,\N you're sure to pass!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.11,0:03:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! This time I'm going to pass!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.37,0:03:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Are you going out?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.17,0:03:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. My friend in Tokyo \Nis also on his "ronin year," {lit: doing ronin - ronin is a wannabe student who is trying for the same exam the second (or rarely more) year in a row}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.19,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so we're going to cheer each other up.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.38,0:03:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you made any progress yet? {lit: cleaned up a little - think he means "fully crammed any themes/questions of the upcoming exam"}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.94,0:03:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, it's a complete dead end.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.77,0:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've also barely started tackling algebra.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.44,0:03:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my confidence\N after failing the first time.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.66,0:03:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll give up on the First and try for the Fourth this time. {yonko = abbreviation of 第四高等学校 - way less prestigious than ichiko}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.12,0:03:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... I'd probably be better off lowering my sights too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.95,0:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're under a lot of pressure from your parents' hopes.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.36,0:03:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can get into the First Higher School. {ichiko}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.14,0:03:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I guess it's time to get serious about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's time.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best, starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.39,0:04:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We'll both give it our all.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.53,0:04:10.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Matsui didn't seem to care much about his studies yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.70,0:04:14.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even though I knew it was pointless to feel reassured by such things,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,my heart still felt at ease. {probably means "to feel reassured that someone else is slacking off so you can too"}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.69,0:04:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Glad you could make it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.32,0:04:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to take the test?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure will. For the First again. {Ichiko}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.63,0:04:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, have a seat.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.41,0:04:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you using this for your prep?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.51,0:04:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything that resembles a textbook here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.39,0:04:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking the test,\N but I don't care if I pass.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't take the test for the First,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,my family will stop sending me money.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.67,0:05:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Kenkichi, want to hit the town tonight?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.39,0:05:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know some great places.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.10,0:05:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never been to Yoshiwara, have you? {red lights district}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, drink this. \NIt'll give you courage!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.87,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold up! I'm going home! \NSee you later!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was shocking.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.34,0:05:32.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It had been a while since I'd seen Sato,\N but he'd become a complete degenerate.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.72,0:05:36.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Matsui had given up on the First, settling for a provincial school in Kanazawa. {ichiko}{miyakoochi = leave the capital = go to kanazawa - kanazawa is where the fourth school (yonko) is}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.77,0:05:39.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Would I wind up like them
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.15,0:05:41.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,if I kept wasting my time too?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There wasn't much time \Nleft before the test.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.04,0:05:46.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I had to make haste.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.12,0:05:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.23,0:05:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenkichi, Sumiko's here.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.48,0:05:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come down and have a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.83,0:06:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I was just thinking of taking a break.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.36,0:06:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kenkichi-san, would you take me\N to the First's school festival this Sunday? {ichiko}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.13,0:06:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The First's school festival? {ichiko}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.75,0:06:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd feel odd, since I'm not a student yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.06,0:06:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be a First Higher School student next year.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.00,0:06:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really have time now.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.93,0:06:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to cram hard.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.82,0:06:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just cram {\i1}all{\i0} the time.\N Don't you need a break sometimes?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.85,0:06:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.40,0:06:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.82,0:06:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What a stick-in-the-mud. {/boring}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.13,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, I'll just have to get someone else to take me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.94,0:06:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.10,0:06:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't affect your studies, Kenkichi?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.79,0:06:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's wonderful!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.63,0:06:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you, Kuno-kun. {assuming kuno is kenkichi's surname?}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.12,0:07:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, I'll show you around.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.66,0:07:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the offer, \Nbut I'm with a guest already.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.57,0:07:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem pretty relaxed. \NI'm sure I'll see you here next year.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.22,0:07:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy yourself, miss.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.08,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that? These First Higher School students are so handsome!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.14,0:07:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be fooled. He got in\N via a recommendation. {was "pulled the strings" in officials}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But he'd like you to think it\N was his own test scores.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.59,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Sumiko-san? {lit: aren't you suffocating}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.39,0:07:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too crowded here.\N Please stay close to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.36,0:07:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let go of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.71,Thought,,0,0,0,,Sumiko's warmth still lingers on my hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.15,0:08:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get into the First Higher School\N and then propose to Sumiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.58,0:08:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.87,0:08:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were studying all day long.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.60,0:08:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.86,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So when will he be coming to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.88,0:08:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The letter from home said he'd be coming right after graduation. {lit: from the countryside}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.15,0:08:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Then he should be here soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.69,0:08:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So Kenji-kun plans to take \Nthe First Higher School test too?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope both of your brothers can get in this year.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.71,0:08:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That would be wonderful!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.64,0:08:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me today!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.37,0:08:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A toast to the scholars getting\N into the First this year! {ichiko}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.52,0:08:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.17,0:08:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenji, are you sure you can get\N into the First Higher School? {lit: do you have confidence in deciding on ichko}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.55,0:08:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.43,0:09:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... But you're going\N to take the test anyway? {without confidence}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.88,0:09:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I hope Kenkichi manages to pass it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.72,0:09:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just taking it as a practice run.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.70,0:09:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you're so relaxed.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good luck to both of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.59,0:09:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.00,0:09:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think you can just read books like that and call it a day? {it's enough for studying}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.15,0:09:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There's nothing for me to worry about.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.98,0:09:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can always take it again next year.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.07,0:09:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsui, are there any empty rooms at the temple?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.17,0:09:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The room next to mine is open. Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.97,0:09:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't concentrate on studying \Nwith my brother around.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.25,0:09:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to pass this test no matter what,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.92,0:10:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and there are only a few weeks left.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.74,0:10:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then. I'll ask around.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.62,0:10:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Kenkichi-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.11,0:10:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.72,0:10:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you. \NI'm his younger brother, Kenji.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.77,0:10:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenkichi's brother?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.30,0:10:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. My brother went to live\N with a friend at the temple.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.88,0:10:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He should come soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.79,0:10:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He always drops by on Mondays.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.09,0:10:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the day Sumiko-san comes over.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.51,0:10:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's you, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.48,0:10:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother wrote me about you.\N He said you were beautiful.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.57,0:10:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you agree, \Nhaving seen for yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.28,0:10:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too good for Kenkichi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.98,0:11:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he is.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.10,0:11:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two laughing about?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.14,0:11:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Were we laughing?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.54,0:11:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I heard you all the way from outside.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.60,0:11:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something funny happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.24,0:11:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.86,0:11:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all. Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.73,0:11:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.27,0:11:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you studying?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.08,0:11:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. I can't seem to get into it. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.73,0:11:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna talk for a while?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.67,0:11:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.62,0:11:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.88,0:11:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not too good. I can't concentrate.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.79,0:12:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you go to see Sumiko-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"Bad, worse, worst."
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.35,0:12:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have studied\N English grammar more. {??? no idea what he means and what "bad/worse" has to do with sumiko; lit: I should've looked at the english grammar here; was "at least it gives me an opportunity to practice my english" in officials}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.07,0:12:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, study and romance just don't mix.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.57,0:12:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you solve this one?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A geometric proof?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.72,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone tried it at the cram school,\N but no one got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.80,0:12:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you shouldn't rush.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.10,0:12:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's impossible\N to solve immediately.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.40,0:12:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Let's see...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.14,0:12:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! You got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.08,0:12:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.31,0:12:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a genius!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.70,0:12:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It took all day, but I finally got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.15,0:12:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.61,0:13:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.07,0:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kenkichi!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.38,0:13:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumiko-san. Are you going home already?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.04,0:13:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I came over early today,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.50,0:13:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,since I knew I'd be busy this afternoon.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.22,0:13:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And where are you going, Kenji?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.32,0:13:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.45,0:13:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When I told Kenji I was going home,\N he offered to walk me back,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.15,0:13:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,since he needed to shop \Nfor some supplies there too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.20,0:13:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out of tally sheets, so I was going to get\N some straw paper. I'll be back soon. {calculation form; tally sheet}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.08,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Goodbye, then, Sumiko-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.00,0:13:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So long.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.71,0:14:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry you missed Sumiko-san. {/couldn't talk to}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.79,0:14:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't bother me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.44,0:14:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, are your studies going well?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.05,0:14:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, more or less.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.42,0:14:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you solve this problem?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.32,0:14:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Geometry?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A proof problem, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.47,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've got it. Is this right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.23,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.83,0:14:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the opposite of the sample problem in the workbook, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.95,0:14:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.01,0:14:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The exams are only a few days off.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.11,0:14:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Good luck to both of us.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.07,0:14:56.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I was suddenly overcome by anxiety and unease, and I couldn't stand it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.58,0:15:01.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Had all my studying been for nothing?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, you're burning up.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.44,0:15:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenkichi, I'm so sorry to have to call you here the day before the test.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, but what's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.28,0:15:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.16,0:15:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Best not to push him too hard. {assuming he talks about kenji, not sister}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.08,0:15:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, he only planned \Nto use this exam as a practice run.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.92,0:15:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I'd taken better care of him.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.01,0:15:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I tell our father? {/apologize to - for kenji failing to go to exam}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.01,0:15:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.59,0:15:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't prevent someone getting sick.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.38,0:15:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Father will understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope his fever \Ngoes down by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.80,0:16:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I help you? \NI'm Yatabe, the Dean.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.31,0:16:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sir. My brother's taking the test right now,\N and that's what worries me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.84,0:16:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He caught a fever yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.39,0:16:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him it'd be better for him \Nto skip the exam this year,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.79,0:16:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but he just wouldn't listen to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.73,0:16:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid he might collapse up there \Nand disturb the other students,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.25,0:16:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,so I have a rickshaw here \Nwaiting for him.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.39,0:16:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know your brother's test number?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.05,0:16:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's number 16 in division 3.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.15,0:16:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Dean!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.64,0:17:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.57,0:17:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 16, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.55,0:17:13.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,Kenji came to the test?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.97,0:17:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Then you should just relax and do your best.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.47,0:17:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. He seems to be doing fine and making good progress. {/and writing answers}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.36,0:17:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My, is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.33,0:17:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your support, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.15,0:17:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I must issue a warning to you all.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.86,0:17:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not let your blank forms hang from the edge of your desk.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I need to explain further.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.40,0:17:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You! I'm disqualifying you! \NLeave the premises at once!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.86,0:17:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch! Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.08,0:17:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I was about to leave anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.79,0:18:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote all the answers ages ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.68,0:18:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrote all the answers? \NIt's blank!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.16,0:18:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want to see me about?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.83,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in love with Sumiko-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.84,0:18:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious about this.\N I want to marry her in the future.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.43,0:18:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.79,0:18:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If possible, I'd like to get engaged \Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.15,0:18:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you act as my intermediary?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.19,0:18:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.59,0:18:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the least, let's wait until you're accepted at the First Higher School. {ichiko}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.44,0:19:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll post the results soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.37,0:19:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenji was sick, so he probably failed.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure you passed.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.14,0:19:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the results are official,\N I'll talk to Sumiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.34,0:19:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.18,0:19:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.62,0:19:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.75,0:19:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.06,0:19:45.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'm not there!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.15,0:19:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It can't be! {I assume because he didn't find his name}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And Kenji?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.09,0:20:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.43,0:20:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that possible?! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.94,0:20:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenkichi...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.33,0:20:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Kenji seen the results already?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.00,0:20:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.41,0:20:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a student at the First Higher School now! That's great!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.62,0:20:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish my brother had made it too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.76,0:20:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well. He simply didn't have it in him. {lit: didn't have the strength}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.73,0:20:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just happy that you made it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.75,0:21:19.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Driven solely by the desire to escape despair, I drank myself blind. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.57,0:21:25.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And before I knew it, \NI had completely degraded myself. {lit: disgraced my soul}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:37.70,Song,,0,0,0,,I write a letter to my loved one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:44.62,Song,,0,0,0,,I write and tear it, tear it, and write again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:51.17,Song,,0,0,0,,I throw the rolled up paper at the window
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.17,0:22:58.34,Song,,0,0,0,,It's raining outside, just like the tears on my cheeks
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.45,0:23:06.22,Song,,0,0,0,,Life is a sea, youth is a boat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.22,0:23:13.29,Song,,0,0,0,,My love, please come and save me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.29,0:23:15.71,Song,,0,0,0,,S.O.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.60,0:23:18.82,Song,,0,0,0,,S.O.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.46,0:23:26.97,Song,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm sinking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.97,0:23:36.39,Song,,0,0,0,,Not a single star in sight, in the sea of ​​sadness
